HEADWORD: Greeze
<hw>Greeze</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A step. See
<er>Gree</er>, a step.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The top of the ladder, or first <qex>greeze</qex>, is this.</q>
<rj><qau>Latimer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Greffier</ent>⟦br⟧
